node.text:
🤟🖤⚡️ #Repost @kamasiwashington with @make_repost
・・・
My version of MY FRIEND Of MISERY from The Metallica Blacklist Album is out today on all platforms. Thank you so much for having me as part of this special project @metallica!! All profits from this song go to Metallica’s All Within My Hands Foundation and @theworldstage in Leimert Park! Link in bio. 

It was so dope to have @robtrujillo and @kirkhammett join us for the live rendition @hollywoodbowl last month! 

🎥: @nesanetabegaze
